summary: A ENB with the best performance for skyrim. full of color and vibrance for people who want a nice looking game without compromising performance.
descriptionHtml:
[IMG]http://i821.photobucket.com/albums/zz132/Bradley_Kefford/title.png[/IMG]
This is a very performance friendly ENB mod reimagined from my DuluxeColor.

 [youtube]n_5MywwfYwI[/youtube]          [youtube]RNKFudi2Q9M[/youtube]

[IMG]http://i821.photobucket.com/albums/zz132/Bradley_Kefford/Features-2.png[/IMG]
These features are compared to my old ENB mod
-50% better performance
-20% more colour 
-Compatible with most mods

[IMG]http://i821.photobucket.com/albums/zz132/Bradley_Kefford/Install.png[/IMG]
Install all contents from folder into Steam/Steamapps/common/Skyrim
author: Countercruel
